text: "A Small Victory" is a 1992 song by Faith No More. It is the second single from their fourth studio album Angel Dust. It went to number 11 in the Billboard Alternative Airplay, number 17 in Finland, number 29 in the United Kingdom and number 84 in Australia. ==Track lists== ==References== Category:1992 songs Category:Faith No More songs Category:Alternative rock songs
